{
  "texts": [
    "The main task order was randomized for each participant.",
    "In each main task, the participants performed the following three subtasks for each of the allocated themes: (1) pre-questionnaire, (2) decision-making, and (3) post-questionnaire tasks.",
    "In the pre-questionnaire task, the participants ranked their interest and knowledge of each main task theme using a sevenpoint Likert scale (1, not at all; 7, very much).",
